<div id="classDescription">
CFlexWidget embeds a Flex 3.x application into a page.
<br/><br/>
To use CFlexWidget, set <?php echo CHtml::link('name', array('/site/doc', 'view' => 'CFlexWidget', '#' => 'name')); ?> to be the Flex application name
(without the .swf suffix), and set <?php echo CHtml::link('baseUrl', array('/site/doc', 'view' => 'CFlexWidget', '#' => 'baseUrl')); ?> to be URL (without the ending slash)
of the directory containing the SWF file of the Flex application.</div>
